⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Morgott
node ER · ER · ⟦Morgott:ER:35876b⟧

WHO   — Morgott — the despised son who defended the Order that scorned him
WHAT  — Son of Marika and Godfrey, born an Omen — horned, accursed, raised shackled in the sewers beneath Leyndell.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: Leyndell, the royal capital, and Stormveil's veiled threshold  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Alone among the demigods he stayed loyal, the last defender of an Order that never loved him.
HOW   — Veiled as Margit, the Fell Omen, he repels Tarnished at Stormveil; unveiled as the Omen King, he holds the royal capital against all comers.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The Order scorned him from birth, and he guarded it to his last breath.

